By: St Louis de Montfort
---
God has never made and formed but one enmity; but it is an
irreconcilable one, which shall endure and grow even to the end. It is
between Mary. His worthy Mother, and the devil -- between the children
and the servants of the Blessed Virgin, and the children and tools of
Lucifer.
